body_html:
And this is my command to compile tflite files through toco.

bazel run tensorflow/contrib/lite/toco:toco --
--input_file=/Users/jyy/model/frozen_inference_graph.pb
--output_file=/Users/jyy/model/wechat.tflite
--input_shapes=1,128,128,3
--input_arrays=normalized_input_image_tensor
--output_arrays='TFLite_Detection_PostProcess','TFLite_Detection_PostProcess:1','TFLite_Detection_PostProcess:2','TFLite_Detection_PostProcess:3'
--inference_type=FLOAT
--allow_custom_ops

body:
And this is my command to compile tflite files through toco. 

bazel run tensorflow/contrib/lite/toco:toco -- \
--input_file=/Users/jyy/model/frozen_inference_graph.pb \
--output_file=/Users/jyy/model/wechat.tflite \
--input_shapes=1,128,128,3 \
--input_arrays=normalized_input_image_tensor \
--output_arrays='TFLite_Detection_PostProcess','TFLite_Detection_PostProcess:1','TFLite_Detection_PostProcess:2','TFLite_Detection_PostProcess:3' \
--inference_type=FLOAT \
--allow_custom_ops
